    "item3223": "Life-Draining Gauntlets Level 6+ Rare Lvl 6 1,800 gp Lvl 26 1,125,000 gp Lvl 16 45,000 gp Hands Slot Property You gain a +2 item bonus to necrotic damage rolls. Level 16: +4 item bonus. Level 26: +6 item bonus. Utility Power ✦ Daily (No Action) Trigger: You hit a creature with an attack and deal necrotic damage to it. Effect: You gain temporary hit points equal to 4 + the gauntlets' level. Mordenkainen's Magnificent Emporium, page(s) 66.",
    "item1756": "Luckbender Gloves Level 6+ Uncommon Lvl 6 1,800 gp Lvl 16 45,000 gp Hands Slot Power ✦ Encounter (Free Action) Use this power after you make a damage roll for a melee weapon attack. Reroll one damage die, using the second result even if it's lower. Level 16: Reroll any two damage dice. Adventurer's Vault, page(s) 136.",
    "item2134": "Rampaging Slayer's Gloves Level 6+ Uncommon Lvl 6 1,800 gp Lvl 26 1,125,000 gp Lvl 16 45,000 gp Hands Slot Property You gain a +4 item bonus to damage rolls for attacks from your Rampage class feature. Level 16: Gain a +8 item bonus to damage Level 26: Gain a +16 item bonus to damage Power ✦ Daily (Free Action) Trigger: You hit with an attack that uses your Rampage class feature. Effect: The attack deals 2[W] extra damage. Dragon Magazine 380, page(s) 32.",
    "item2168": "Reparation Apparatus Level 6 Uncommon Hands Slot 1,800 gp Property When you use a power that allows a construct to spend a healing surge to regain hit points, that creature regains an additional 2d6 hit points. When you use an encounter power or a daily power to grant temporary hit points to a construct ally, that creature gains an additional 2d6 temporary hit points. Dragon Magazine 365, page(s) 15.",
