    "item1431": "Gloves of Eldritch Admixture Level 8+ Uncommon Lvl 8 3,400 gp Lvl 28 2,125,000 gp Lvl 18 85,000 gp Hands Slot Requirement: Warlock Property When you deal extra damage as a result of your Warlock's Curse, you can choose that damage to be acid, cold, or fire (or leave it untyped). Power (Acid, Cold, Fire) ✦ Encounter, 5 Charges/Day (Free Action) The next attack you make this turn deals extra damage depending on how many charges you spend: 1 charge, 1d6 damage; 2 charges, 2d6 damage; 5 charges, 3d6 damage. This extra damage can be acid, cold, or fire damage. Level 18: 1 charge, 1d8 damage; 2 charges, 2d8 damage; 5 charges, 3d8 damage. Level 28: 1 charge, 1d10 damage; 2 charges, 2d10 damage; 5 charges, 3d10 damage. Adventurer's Vault, page(s) 134.",
