    "item1156": "Eagle Eye Goggles Level 2+ Uncommon Lvl 2 520 gp Lvl 22 325,000 gp Lvl 12 13,000 gp Head Slot Property Gain a +1 item bonus to ranged basic attack rolls. Level 12: Gain a +2 item bonus Level 22: Gain a +3 item bonus Adventurer's Vault, page(s) 140.",
