    "item3226": "Eyes of Charming Level 6+ Rare Lvl 6 1,800 gp Lvl 26 1,125,000 gp Lvl 16 45,000 gp Head Slot Property You gain a +2 item bonus to Bluff checks and Diplomacy checks. Level 16: +4 item bonus. Level 26: +6 item bonus. ➶ Attack Power (Charm) ✦ Daily (Standard Action) Attack: Ranged 5 (one creature); the eyes' level + 5 vs. Will Hit: The target is dominated (save ends). The target is not aware that you used this power against it. Mordenkainen's Magnificent Emporium, page(s) 67.",
