    "item923": "Cloak of the Walking Wounded Level 4+ Uncommon Lvl 4 +1 840 gp Lvl 19 +4 105,000 gp Lvl 9 +2 4,200 gp Lvl 24 +5 525,000 gp Lvl 14 +3 21,000 gp Lvl 29 +6 2,625,000 gp Neck Slot Enhancement Bonus: Fortitude, Reflex, and Will Property If you use your second wind while bloodied, you can expend two healing surges instead of one (gaining hit points from both). Adventurer's Vault, page(s) 151.",
    "item937": "Collar of Recovery Level 4+ Common Lvl 4 +1 840 gp Lvl 19 +4 105,000 gp Lvl 9 +2 4,200 gp Lvl 24 +5 525,000 gp Lvl 14 +3 21,000 gp Lvl 29 +6 2,625,000 gp Neck Slot Enhancement Bonus: Fortitude, Reflex, and Will Property Gain extra hit points equal to this item's enhancement bonus when you spend a healing surge to regain hit points. Adventurer's Vault, page(s) 151.",
    "item1095": "Disk of Energy Resistance Level 4+ Uncommon Lvl 4 +1 840 gp Lvl 19 +4 105,000 gp Lvl 9 +2 4,200 gp Lvl 24 +5 525,000 gp Lvl 14 +3 21,000 gp Lvl 29 +6 2,625,000 gp Neck Slot (attached component) Enhancement Bonus: Fortitude, Reflex, and Will Requirement: You must have the living construct racial trait to use this item. Power ✦ Daily (Immediate Reaction) Trigger: You are hit by a fire, force, lightning, psychic, radiant, or thunder attack. Effect: You gain resist 5 against one of the attack's triggering damage types until the end of the encounter. Level 14: Resist 10. Level 19: Resist 10. Level 24: Resist 20. Level 29: Resist 20. Eberron Player's Guide, page(s) 114.",
    "item3420": "Earthmother Torc Level 4+ Uncommon Lvl 4 +1 840 gp Lvl 19 +4 105,000 gp Lvl 9 +2 4,200 gp Lvl 24 +5 525,000 gp Lvl 14 +3 21,000 gp Lvl 29 +6 2,625,000 gp Neck Slot Enhancement Bonus: Fortitude, Reflex, and Will Property You are immune to diseases transmitted by shapechanger attacks. Utility Power ✦ Daily (No Action) Trigger: A shapechanger is hit by your attack. Effect: The shapechanger cannot regain hit points and cannot use polymorph powers (save ends both). Dungeon Magazine 196, Dungeon Magazine 210.",
    "item1220": "Essence of the Scout Level 4+ Uncommon Lvl 4 +1 840 gp Lvl 19 +4 105,000 gp Lvl 9 +2 4,200 gp Lvl 24 +5 525,000 gp Lvl 14 +3 21,000 gp Lvl 29 +6 2,625,000 gp Neck Slot (embedded component) Enhancement Bonus: Fortitude, Reflex, and Will Requirement: You must have the living construct racial trait to use this item. Property You gain a +2 item bonus to Stealth checks. Power ✦ Daily (Minor Action) You gain a +5 power bonus to your next Stealth check made before the end of your next turn. Eberron Player's Guide, page(s) 114.",
