    "item2001": "Orc's-Eye Amulet Level 8+ Uncommon Lvl 8 +2 3,400 gp Lvl 23 +5 425,000 gp Lvl 13 +3 17,000 gp Lvl 28 +6 2,125,000 gp Lvl 18 +4 85,000 gp Neck Slot Enhancement Bonus: Fortitude, Reflex, and Will Power ✦ Encounter (Immediate Reaction) Trigger: An ally within 10 squares of you bloodies an enemy. Effect: The ally gains temporary hit points equal to 3 + the amulet's enhancement bonus. Level 18 or 23: 6 + the amulet's enhancement bonus. Level 28: 9 + the amulet's enhancement bonus. Adventurer's Vault 2, page(s) 67.",
    "item2020": "Pavise Charm Level 8+ Uncommon Lvl 8 +2 3,400 gp Lvl 23 +5 425,000 gp Lvl 13 +3 17,000 gp Lvl 28 +6 2,125,000 gp Lvl 18 +4 85,000 gp Neck Slot Enhancement Bonus: Fortitude, Reflex, and Will Power ✦ Daily (Minor Action) You gain a +2 power bonus to AC and Reflex until you leave your current space. Adventurer's Vault 2, page(s) 101.",
    "item2021": "Peacemaker's Periapt Level 8+ Uncommon Lvl 8 +2 3,400 gp Lvl 23 +5 425,000 gp Lvl 13 +3 17,000 gp Lvl 28 +6 2,125,000 gp Lvl 18 +4 85,000 gp Neck Slot Enhancement Bonus: Fortitude, Reflex, and Will Property Gain an item bonus to Diplomacy checks equal to the periapt's enhancement bonus. Power (Charm) ✦ Daily (Minor Action) Choose a target within 10 squares of you. That target takes a -2 penalty to melee and ranged attack rolls against you for the remainder of the encounter or until you attack it (whichever comes first). Adventurer's Vault, page(s) 153.",
    "item2033": "Periapt of Recovery Level 8+ Common Lvl 8 +2 3,400 gp Lvl 23 +5 425,000 gp Lvl 13 +3 17,000 gp Lvl 28 +6 2,125,000 gp Lvl 18 +4 85,000 gp Neck Slot Enhancement Bonus: Fortitude, Reflex, and Will Property Gain a +2 item bonus to death saving throws. Adventurer's Vault, page(s) 153.",
